* `src/ui/App.tsx`

  * toolbar + modal wiring, wallpaper state, templates modal structure, ad slot placement
* `src/ui/components/AccordionCardEditor.tsx`

  * fold/open behavior, card selector, layout selector, internal mini-tabs, runtime stability
* `src/ui/components/PreviewPane.tsx`

  * floating render mode, preview behavior, alignment / line rendering (currently failing build)
* `src/ui/styles.css`

  * glass styling, modal sizing/scroll, removal of canvas borders, ad slot positioning, dark dropdown options

