## Current Status

* UI direction and most layout goals reached visually.
* Remaining blocker is **a PreviewPane.tsx syntax error** preventing production build.
* After fixing PreviewPane, final polish items are mostly CSS-level (spacing/locking boundaries), unless further runtime issues appear.

